Description: Aptura OS system policy and security defaults
 Conservative defaults for a daily-driver desktop: AppArmor enforcing, UFW
 default-deny incoming with no SSH server, automatic security updates, sane
 sysctl tweaks, the SDDM Aptura theme/session, and privacy-respecting
 NetworkManager/journald settings.
